					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1929896#post-2662799</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1929896/scp-2462#post-2662799</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 29 Sep 2016 17:14:41 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Communism will win</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>617958</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I haven't &#8212; I'm used to not doing it, since my titles are usually more of an afterthought. I'll do that now, though.</p> <p>And nobody really knows exactly how rare the corpse flower is, because it's so incredibly hard to find &#8212; it's only visible to the naked eye for a few days per year while it's budding or blooming. It's assumed to be critically endangered because its habitat is being thoroughly wrecked by logging &#8212; nobody actually has anything resembling a headcount of these things.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
